   162â†’**REMEMBER: This is an INFOGRAPHIC - Visual Appeal is CRITICAL!**
   163â†’
   164â†’1. **Infographic Visual Design**:
   165â†’   - INFOGRAPHIC-STYLE: Modern, clean, colorful, and engaging layout
