   189â†’
   190â†’4. **Color Coding Guidelines**:
   191â†’   For HEALTH parameters (Cognition, Focus, Emotional Regulation, Learning, Creativity):
   192â†’   - High (3/3): #38A169 (Green) - Excellent performance
