   276â†’7. Each subparameter must have the EXACT score (0 or 1) from the input data
   277â†’8. Icons should be colorful brain-related emojis: ğŸ§  ğŸ’¡ ğŸ¯ âš¡ ğŸ˜Œ ğŸ“š ğŸ¨ ğŸŒŸ âš–ï¸ ğŸ”¥ or similar
   278â†’9. Make interpretations ultra-relatable - focus on real-world meaning, avoid EEG jargon
